page_0:
"The elements are turning against us! Not a day passes without the ground trembling violently. The eastern shrine got completely submerged by the inexplicably rising seawater, and aggressive fire elementals have started appearing in the alleys of our city.

I think this must be what happened to Karath'din. Centuries ago Va-Toran arrived through the Celestial Gate and died at its steps. What he managed to tell the priests before he passed away was very similar to what we are experiencing now."